    <note>Peng(1) Ruli [1400] Jinshi # 1. His ancestors moved from Jiangning, Jinling to Poyang (see other Jiangxi Peng). His unnamed father, Peng(1) A [4190], was a Raozhou clerk (li). His younger brother, Rulin [3708], was once recommended by Zeng(1) Bu [1707]. Another younger brother, Rufang [3707], used Ruli's yin to enter the civil service. Ruli was Wu(3) Cai's [7397] father-in-law (twice: sororate) XCB, 287.16b, 293.5a; Du Dagui, 'zhong,' 31.4b. CBD, 4, 2953.</note>
